fs2ram (0.3.7) UNRELEASED; urgency=low

  * The conffile fs2ram.conf is now in /etc/fs2ram/.
  * fs2ram is quiet during startup/shutdown (show only error).
  * Some debian packaging stuff.
  * English rewording.
  * Some cleaning.
  * Switch from the exec ... < construction to while ... done <.
  * /var/log, /var/run, /var/cache are now handled by default (work out
    of the box).
  * Fix the return code for the do_mountpoint() function.
  * move the unmount scripts from /usr/share/fs2ram to /lib/fs2ram.
  * init: add syslog-ng to X-Stop-After.

 -- Philippe Le Brouster <plb@nebkha.net>  Wed, 20 Oct 2010 15:05:47 +0200

